<br>
Nice idea, but probably too easy, and doesn't create enough conflict with other player characters.  More likely it would be something like this:<br>
<br>
 - Quest mob is on Friends of Cabbage faction, which everyone starts low dubious to.<br>
<br>
 - Turn in four cabbages (must be the foraged type) to get a faction adjustment of +1 Friends of Cabbage.<br>
<br>
 - When you're max ally with Friends of Cabbage, you can hand the NPC 1000pp, and an item obtained by combining a Ring of the Ancients, a Red Dragon Scale, a Green Dragon Scale, and a White Dragon Scale in the heart container from Ragefire.  After that's done, you get your spell, which is no drop.<br>
